p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e06\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eOK but most people wish they could do this!\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10472591104/h53DB26E2/al-show-up-with-my-mom-and-have-her-answer-all-questions\" id=\"_r_a_10472591104\" width=\"800\" height=\"390\" alt=\"al... Show up with my mom and have her answer all the questions for me.\" title=\"OK but most people wish they could do this!\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e07\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eThis one could also get you hired depending on the workplace!\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10472591872/h5750DB2F/job-because-who-wouldnt-want-work-with-dude-would-show-up-an-interview-with-bird-on-their-shoulder\" id=\"_r_a_10472591872\" width=\"800\" height=\"1000\" alt=\"chadster1979 Showing up to interview with a pet parrot on your shoulder does not blow the interview. My wife worked for a popular online shoe retailer that starts with a Z and interviewed a guy who showed up like this. She gave him the job, because, who wouldn\u0026#39;t want to work with a dude that would show up to an interview with a bird on their shoulder.\" title=\"This one could also get you hired depending on the workplace!\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cl